  "texts": [
    "The extracted evidence is sent to the QA Agent, which returns the answer a i.",
    "This answer is added to the history H i, and the next iteration begins.",
    "The system maintains state throughout the reasoning trajectory, allowing each agent to condition on the evolving context.",
    "This modular design enables flexible, step-by-step",
